# How to run

### Run the server and then run the client.

1- Command to run the server in a terminal
```bash
make run-server
```

2- Command to run the client in another terminal
```bash
make run-client
```

3- Follow the instructions that appear in the console on the client

### If you want to delete all the unnecessary files and restart the project run the following command.
Command to clean the files
```bash
make clean
```